{"tid":2132584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鞭屍系列］【武漢肺炎肆虐】司徒法正算計到有疾病困擾 預計年中情況會好轉","createTime":"2020-07-30T12:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T13:06:44.000Z","uid":181064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11fc7d5c209943d699fee09de93092bbb5b18569","tid":2132584,"uid":181064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"更新時間 (HKT): 2020.01.24 21:05<br />\n<br />\n玄學家司徒法正今日到觀塘接受面包台節目訪問，談到年近歲晚，不少善信及客戶都找他幫忙還神和祈福，剛剛更從美國出席完講座，他說：「可能最近個市唔係咁好，好多人都想聽下有咩方法，我就建議大家採取主動，有危先有機。特別今年係屬金水，從事金融嘅都會有一定嘅機會。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n談到最近武漢肺炎肆虐，司徒法正表示從術數上來說已預計到今年會有疾病困擾，他說：「今年更加係庚子年，每到庚子年都有一啲大事發生，所以建議大家今年萬事小心，<span class=\"red\">預計到年中情況就會好轉</span>。」<br />\n採訪：曹家誠<br />\n攝影：仇志德<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200124/JLYBUS2TEQHOA4NRU2XM23WZD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200124%2FJLYBUS2TEQHOA4NRU2XM23WZD4%2F&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=05334695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200124%2FJLYBUS2TEQHOA4NRU2XM23WZD4%2F&h=896515ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200124/JLYBUS2TEQHOA4NRU2XM23WZD4/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmmZP6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmmZP6v.jpg&h=2bfc418b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06531123072243ee39808b